{"tid":124517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無錫女會計被騙136萬　WeChat「公司群組」竟全是騙子","createTime":"2017-02-17T16:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T16:13:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99914955e517f50eb6f857c43af062e6d5c090d8","tid":124517,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/無錫女會計被騙136萬-wechat-公司群組-竟全是騙子-113000499.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%84%A1%E9%8C%AB%E5%A5%B3%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99136%E8%90%AC-wechat-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84-%E7%AB%9F%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E9%A8%99%E5%AD%90-113000499.html&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8Dxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=6d3f15e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/無錫女會計被騙136萬-wechat-公司群組-竟全是騙子-113000499.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2017-02-16/a1c71ed0-f493-11e6-9a71-055a8cad5bd4_5-WeChat-Moments.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-02-16%2Fa1c71ed0-f493-11e6-9a71-055a8cad5bd4_5-WeChat-Moments.jpg&h=47a42634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報導】無錫一名女會計遭「同事」騙取136萬，其後發現WeChat「公司群組」內，除了自己其他人竟全是騙子。<br />\n<br />\n　　原來有騙子冒充公司領導，將該公司的會計員工加為WeChat好友，接著又將錢姓女會計職員拉進以公司命名的WeChat群組，錢小姐發現群組內全是公司員工，便誤以為進了工作群。騙子以退還客戶保證金、支付定金等理由，騙取該錢小姐兩次轉賬，總計136萬元，但是群組內再無動靜。<br />\n<br />\n　　經過警方偵查，兩名負責取錢的詐騙嫌犯落網，而「主腦」仍在追捕中。昨日，無錫濱湖法院開庭審理了此案，並將擇日宣判。"}]}